  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_5_4364-4392",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4364-4392",
      "markText": "相门翩翩公子，江湖落落狂生；清代第一才士，千古伤心词人。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4364&rangeEnd=4392",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4364&rangeEnd=4392"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_6_15397-15461",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "15397-15461",
      "markText": "人生若只如初见，何事秋风悲画扇。等闲变却故人心，却道故人心易变。骊山语罢清宵半。泪雨霖铃终不怨。何如薄幸锦衣郎，比翼连枝当日愿。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15397&rangeEnd=15461",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15397&rangeEnd=15461"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_8_12652-12724",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "12652-12724",
      "markText": "当时只道是寻常”——真正的痛，不是号啕大哭，不是捶胸顿足，也不是呼天抢地，也许只是一声轻轻的叹息，也许只是长久的沉默之后，脸颊上淌落的一行清泪。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12652&rangeEnd=12724",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12652&rangeEnd=12724"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_7_5096-5157",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5096-5157",
      "markText": "而卢氏作为一个妻子更令人敬重的地方，是她甚至还帮着纳兰收藏那些凄婉动人的爱情词，哪怕那些动人的词句是写给另外一个女人的……",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5096&rangeEnd=5157",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5096&rangeEnd=5157"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_8_12762-12837",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "12762-12837",
      "markText": "当拥有幸福的时候，人人都会觉得这样的幸福很平常，平常得随处可见，平常得甚至让人轻易地忽略了它的存在。只有当你失去它的时候，你才会明白，什么是真正的痛。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12762&rangeEnd=12837",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12762&rangeEnd=12837"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_5_1378-1393",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1378-1393",
      "markText": "我是人间惆怅客，知君何事泪纵横",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1378&rangeEnd=1393",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1378&rangeEnd=1393"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_5_2398-2443",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2398-2443",
      "markText": "《红楼梦》中最重要的人物——男主人公贾宝玉的原型，就被认为是纳兰明珠的长子——纳兰性德了。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2398&rangeEnd=2443",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2398&rangeEnd=2443"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_5_9731-9766",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9731-9766",
      "markText": "一个人没有选择出身的自由，可是任何人都有权自由选择自己向往的生活方式。",
      "totalCount": 77,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9731&rangeEnd=9766",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9731&rangeEnd=9766"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_9_9213-9276",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "9213-9276",
      "markText": "纳兰的悲剧，也许就在于他懂得了什么是爱情，正因为他太懂爱情，所以在失去爱情的时候，他才会比别人更痛苦，更不能从悲伤中解脱出来。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9213&rangeEnd=9276",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9213&rangeEnd=9276"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_8_10769-10827",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10769-10827",
      "markText": "真正高明的化妆应该是明净的，清澈的，是和人的整体气质协调的，它会让人忽略掉化妆的痕迹，而对和谐的自然美留下深刻印象。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10769&rangeEnd=10827",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10769&rangeEnd=10827"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_8_11619-11641",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11619-11641",
      "markText": "什么是悲剧？悲剧就是将最美的东西毁灭给人看！",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11619&rangeEnd=11641",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11619&rangeEnd=11641"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_11_4702-4796",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "4702-4796",
      "markText": "徐乾学兄弟三人在当时号称“昆山三徐”：老大徐乾学是康熙九年（1670）庚戌科探花，授翰林院编修；老二徐秉义是康熙十二年（1673）癸丑科探花；老三徐元文是顺治十六年（1659）己亥科状元。",
      "totalCount": 66,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4702&rangeEnd=4796",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4702&rangeEnd=4796"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_8_8329-8422",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8329-8422",
      "markText": "谁念西风独自凉。萧萧黄叶闭疏窗。沉思往事立残阳。 被酒莫惊春睡重，赌书消得泼茶香。当时只道是寻常。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8329&rangeEnd=8422",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8329&rangeEnd=8422"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_3_2895-2944",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2895-2944",
      "markText": "屈原是盘旋郁结而炽热的；李清照是婉转多思而细腻的；陆游是慷慨悲凉而执着的，纳兰是多情凄苦而低徊的。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37100263&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2895&rangeEnd=2944",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/196329d072361ae71964727?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2895&rangeEnd=2944"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37100263_4_1525-1604",
